  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to test two regimens of mifegyne and cytotec for medical
      abortion. The investigators hypothesize that administration of both medications during one
      hospital visit will not compromise effectiveness.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
